        ; however, it guarantees that they are in some cases. We can thus see
        <math>
            <msup>
                <mrow>
                    <mrow><mi mathvariant="-tex-caligraphic">D</mi></mrow>
                </mrow>
                <mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow>
            </msup>
        </math>
        as an “organizational type” of
        <math>
            <msup>
                <mrow>
                    <mrow><mi mathvariant="-tex-caligraphic">D</mi></mrow>
                </mrow>
                <mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow>
            </msup>
