        . In a given situation, when the constraints involved are largely conserved, we can argue that
        <math>
            <msup>
                <mrow>
                    <mrow><mi mathvariant="-tex-caligraphic">D</mi></mrow>
                </mrow>
                <mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow>
            </msup>
